Package: khisr
Title: An R Client to Retrieve Data from DHIS2
Description: Provides a user-friendly interface for interacting with
        the District Health Information Software 2 (DHIS2) instance. It
        streamlines data retrieval, empowering researchers, analysts,
        and healthcare professionals to obtain and utilize data
        efficiently.
